Subject: Re: [T2] RE: Brake Booster Removal


Correct me here if I am wrong but isn't Brake fluid in the booster a sign
of a leaking master cylinder? You should rebuild or replace that master
cylinder before the fluid destroys your booster, which is even more
expensive. Master cylinders are easy to rebuild and I believe cheap to
replace.

