Mine had brake fluid in it.

Maybe 1/4 cup.


Rinsed it twice with a bottle of alcohol each
time.  Shook it out let it dry over night...hope it works fine<grin>.

If it worked with the brake fluid in it, I suspect it would work just fine
without it also.

Cheers, dave

